reviewText:
Face Behind the Mask was released in 1979 and was directed by Chan Chi Hwa. FBM stars Lo Lieh,Yueh Wah,Sung Jung Chi,Hsu Feng, Lee Man Tai,Woo Kei,Go Ming.

FBM is mostly a Taiwanese production with a few Hong Kong actors.
I rate this film a 3 star effort no fabulous sword lighting techniques in this film a good story and 2 great stars Lo Liel and Yueh Hua.
